{
  "stem": "21308.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I had a wonderful headmaster who kept an eye on me, quite frankly, until he died.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I always likened him to Dr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Arnold of Rugby, who was the great educationalist of Victorian times.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I think Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "A.J. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Kidd ?] was his equal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we all had tremendous respect for him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the same goes for our farmers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It's-- it was an agricultural town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And our farmers, in fact, employed most of the men and a lot of us boys.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "From the age of 9, one got a job whenever there was a holiday.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I was very fortunate enough to get a job with a family, a yeoman family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And in fact, I'm still in touch with the family to this day, although I now live on the other side of the world.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he was a professional soldier, until he did his time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then he developed with animals.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You must realize that there was a depression on, and lots of little farmers couldn't afford a veterinary surgeon.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father did a lot of veterinary work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Mother worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we all worked, and we got by.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, my older brother was Bill, who's dead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He died as a result of war service.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jack, my younger brother, who was very good at athletics-- in fact, he won the Victor Ludorum Cup in school-- he was killed in the Royal Air Force in Burma just as the war in the Far East was finishing.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my sister married a soldier who was in the town during the war, and she still lives in the house where the family has lived ever since the house was built.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it's one of a number of houses built by the council before the-- round about 1930.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
